import React from "react";
import {Box, Grid, Typography, Button } from "@material-ui/core"

export default (props)=>( 
<Box py={10} bgcolor="secondary.main" color="white">
<Grid container>
<Grid item xs={10}>
    <Typography variant="h3">HackSpon</Typography>
    <Button variant="contained" color="primary" disableElevation>Post a Sponsor</Button>
</Grid>
</Grid>
</Box>
)
